com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaAction.AylaActionParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaAction.AylaActionParameters
  • 封闭类:
    AylaAction

    public static class AylaAction.AylaActionParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains key / value pairs with information relevant to the action to be performed. For Datapoint action required parameter key is ‘datapoint’. For e.g. "parameters": { "datapoint" : "DATAPOINT(dsn1,prop1) = 70" } For Email action required parameter keys are email_to, email_subject & Email_body. For e.g. "parameters": { "email_body": "Hi there!!", "email_to": [ "abc@xyz.com" ], "email_subject": "Device Updated Notification" }
